init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He says Matt Damon is his soul mate.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They go through a lot of trouble trying to find where the alien went.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They call all the soldiers to come and find Matt Damon and they go on a helicopter.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien then looks at Matt and smiles.
